[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     42[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Encryption at rest specified for S3 (SSE-KMS), DynamoDB (encryption at rest enabled by default), Kinesis (server-side encryption with KMS), SageMaker training and inference (encrypted EBS volumes, KMS-encrypted output), and CloudWatch log groups (configure KMS encryption explicitly). The explicit elevation of CloudWatch log-group KMS configuration is the right call out.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     43[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - VPC enforcement framed correctly for production: "SageMaker training and inference in VPC with VPC endpoints for S3, Kinesis, CloudWatch Logs, and KMS. Required for HIPAA workloads."
