[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     45[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - Synthetic-data discipline in the Sample Data row: "Never use real ED arrival data in dev." The MIMIC-IV-ED reference is correctly hedged with credentialed-access framing, and the synthetic-data generation guidance ("Poisson with hour-of-day intensity plus weekly seasonality plus weather effects plus noise") is the right shape for healthcare-realistic prototyping.
